    "Caw worked as a draughtsman in Glasgow from 1887 to 1889 and then in Edinburgh beginning in 1889, continuing to study science courses intermittently at Heriot-Watt College and art at the Glasgow School of Art and the Royal Scottish Academy School of Art.": [
